WEBVTT

00:00.268 --> 00:02.903
<i>I used to be a spy until...</i>

00:03.003 --> 00:04.370
[ Cellphone rings ]

00:04.397 --> 00:05.864
Man: We got a burn notice
on you. You're blacklisted.

00:05.932 --> 00:07.365
[ Whistles ]

00:07.433 --> 00:09.668
<i>When you're burned,</i>
<i>you've got nothing --</i>

00:09.735 --> 00:11.937
<i>no cash, no credit,</i>
<i>no job history.</i>

00:12.004 --> 00:14.306
<i>You're stuck in whatever city</i>
<i>they decide to dump you in.</i>

00:14.373 --> 00:16.174
- Where am I?
- Miami.

00:16.242 --> 00:18.977
<i>You do whatever work</i>
<i>comes your way.</i>

00:19.045 --> 00:21.012
<i>You rely on anyone</i>
<i>who's still talking to you.</i>

00:21.080 --> 00:22.047
[ Laughs ]

00:22.114 --> 00:23.481
<i>A trigger-happy girlfriend...</i>

00:23.549 --> 00:25.083
Should we shoot them?

00:25.151 --> 00:26.885
<i>...an old friend who used</i>
<i>to inform on you to the FBI...</i>

00:26.953 --> 00:29.621
You know spies --
a bunch of bitchy little girls.

00:29.689 --> 00:31.957
<i>...family, too...</i>
<i>Hey, is that your mom again?</i>

00:32.024 --> 00:33.858
<i>...if you're desperate....</i>
<i>Someone needs your help, Michael.</i>

00:33.926 --> 00:36.962
<i>...and a down-and-out spy</i>
<i>you met along the way.</i>

00:37.029 --> 00:38.596
That's how we do it,
people.

00:38.664 --> 00:41.199
<i>Bottom line --</i>
<i>as long as you're burned,</i>

00:41.267 --> 00:43.001
<i>you're not going anywhere.</i>

00:47.039 --> 00:49.374
[ Whistles ]
Michael: Put the weapon down.

00:51.267 --> 00:52.567
Hands on your head!

00:52.635 --> 00:54.569
Listen to me, Michael.
Gray shot your brother.

00:54.637 --> 00:55.670
He murdered Nate.

00:58.040 --> 01:01.976
I'll hunt you down to the ends
of the earth if I have to.

01:02.044 --> 01:03.745
Then I'll see you there.

01:03.812 --> 01:05.379
Jesse:
There she is.

01:05.447 --> 01:06.981
Bye, sweetheart.

01:09.218 --> 01:11.152
[ Engine turns over ]

01:11.220 --> 01:12.220
[ Sighs ]
Stay beautiful.

01:12.288 --> 01:13.521
I'm sorry, Sam.
Yeah.

01:13.589 --> 01:15.890
I don't want to hear about it,
Mike. Let's just go.

01:15.958 --> 01:17.825
[ Tires squeal ]

01:17.893 --> 01:21.229
So, all this is yours?
Yeah. I'm kind of a big deal.

01:22.898 --> 01:24.666
That's how
I'm able to smuggle

01:24.733 --> 01:26.801
freeloading super-spies
to other countries.

01:28.804 --> 01:30.672
They're in the warehouse!
Schmidt, get out here!

01:36.045 --> 01:38.346
I'll give you guys
new identities, passports,

01:38.414 --> 01:40.548
a free trip
to wherever you want to go.

01:40.616 --> 01:42.483
But you guys may have to foot
some of the bill.

01:42.551 --> 01:44.919
We're getting the passports. We
need to know if you're coming.

01:44.987 --> 01:46.321
Because of you, Mike,

01:46.388 --> 01:47.989
the last time I kissed My Lady,
she was crying.

01:49.458 --> 01:50.825
I'll let you know.

